{"tid":1906781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警哨兵發現！！認住佢！！","createTime":"2020-03-02T07:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T13:02:53.000Z","uid":310881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fad615736828d06d07eeca67303016ebe1639b00","tid":1906781,"uid":310881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/123380702388719/posts/217459432980845/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F123380702388719%2Fposts%2F217459432980845%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=f16356bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/123380702388719/posts/217459432980845/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n「已Fact Check 」<br />\n<br />\n「極常影住手足Set road block」<br />\n<br />\n「行行下Nathan Road、又再行去西洋菜南街，跟住又去麥花臣果邊。已經肯定依一名記者就係黑警既哨兵。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫大家私了呢個記者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但成篇野有乜證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<strong>影Set RB同行來行去？？</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁已經肯定立場哥哥就係黑警哨兵！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好多人share同留言話要私了<br />\n支持杯葛百份<br />\n但唔係黃衛兵到連採訪都要私了嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同Chinazi同藍絲有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">p.s. 問咗記者朋友話唔係<br />\n雖然我冇得撬開比人指控嘅記者個腦FC<br />\n但呢篇野乜證據都冇<br />\n希望大家認住呢啲垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提防黃衛兵風向<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2aebd9a8929a89fd144f94ad6a73388a7d755d65","tid":1906781,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"記者做緊記者做嘅嘢<br />\n佢立場係咁<br />\n手足唯一做到嘅係包密啲<br />\n但如果佢唔係記者<br />\n我相信大家識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed6a84da4988069ff8bab6b54717187d28e22ab","tid":1906781,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"哩度大把人只願意信自己想相信的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abb5b61d47d3f30728c906b6a1cc0d2e4c3fd3d","tid":1906781,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"哩個私了雖然又俾對家做新聞<br />\n但交俾到時嘅手足去判斷啦<br />\n提一提係多人有意識咗嘅<br />\n<br />\n我自己就點都唔忍<br />\n當係扮高尚都好<br />\n唔想做對家一樣嘅野<br />\n<br />\n但網上點搞佢就控制唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3773e9c769b855b406d324faeaca2c9c47316e8c","tid":1906781,"uid":310881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2aebd9a8929a89fd144f94ad6a73388a7d755d65","tid":1906781,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"記者做緊記者做嘅嘢<br />\n佢立場係咁<br />\n手足唯一做到嘅係包密啲<br />\n但如果佢唔係記者<br />\n我相信大家識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:02:53.000Z","msg":"同意 啲人講咗好多次<br />\n如果記者只係影黑警 唔影手足<br />\n咪又係唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}